triples: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaius_Julius_Caesar_(proconsul_of_Asia)> <http://dbpedia.org/property/children> "Julia Major, Julia Minor and Julius Caesar"@en

questions.question: How big is the earth's diameter?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT (( xsd:double(?radius) * 2 ) AS ?diameter) WHERE { res:Earth dbo:meanRadius ?radius }

questions.question: Which museum exhibits The Scream by Munch?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:The_Scream dbo:museum ?uri }

questions.question: Which movies did Kurosawa direct?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:director res:Akira_Kurosawa }

questions.question: Give me a list of all critically endangered birds.
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri ?p WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Bird { ?uri dbo:conservationStatus "CR" } UNION { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Critically_endangered_animals } }

questions.question: Which book has the most pages?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Book ; dbo:numberOfPages ?n } ORDER BY DESC(?n) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

questions.question: What is the area code of Berlin?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?string WHERE { res:Berlin dbo:areaCode ?string }
